data.description: Single family home nestled in the city of North Miami with exceptional curb appeal. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms and an additional space that can be used as a 4th bedroom or efficiency. The kitchen has been tastefully updated, providing a contemporary space. Tile floors throughout to ensure easy maintenance. Natural light floods the interior, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that's perfect for both relaxation and productivity. Backyard offers a private retreat for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding under the open sky. Roof replaced in 2022. Convenient access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and more. This is an exceptional opportunity to own a beautiful home.
